# Environment Variables Example File
# ===================================
# This file documents the environment variables used by the PopoverPro application.
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values as needed.
#
# Currently, the PopoverPro application does not require any environment variables.
# This file exists as part of best practices for project configuration.
#
# Example format:
# VARIABLE_NAME=value
#
# If future features require environment variables, they should be documented here.
